      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Persistence Of the Portraitist</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter from Roberta Oster on Deborah Solomon's Feb 1 profile of artist Chuck Close; photo (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Deborah Solomon sculptures an exquisite portrait of the artist Chuck Close (''The Persistence of the Portraitist,'' Feb. 1). In 1991, I interviewed Close for a TV series. He seemed to be skipping around his studio in his wheelchair, joyfully playing with color and line and space.</p>
        <p>Roberta Oster  Palo Alto, Calif.</p>
      </block>
